Nollywood actor, Jim Iyke has made some revelations about his personal life and struggles. Jim Iyke, in an interview with Chude Jideonwo, revealed that he’s had a failed marriage that no one knows. He also mentioned that he has three children and has sometime in his life cried because he failed woefully in every business. He said: “I’ve had a failed marriage nobody knows, I have three beautiful kids. “I hate to be figured out, once you figure me out, I have nothing else to offer. So, that’s the potency in it; I refuse to be figured out or tamed. “For a long time, every business I involved myself failed woefully.” Video:   A post shared by Chude Jideonwo (@chudeity) 